{"word":"H7965 - שָׁלֹום - shâlôwm - shaw-lome' - [idiom] do","slug":"H7965","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁלֹום</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâlôwm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-lome'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] do"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05DD;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DC;&#x05D5;&#x05DD; - sha&#x0302;lo&#x0302;m  sha&#x0302;lo&#x0302;m</b> - <i>shaw-lome', shaw-lome'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H7999\">H7999</a>; <i>safe</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>well</i>, <i>happy</i>, <i>friendly</i>; also (abstractly) <i>welfare</i>, that is, health, prosperity, peace: -  X do, familiar, X fare, favour, + friend, X greet, (good) health, (X perfect, such as be at) peace (-able, -ably), prosper (-ity, -ous), rest, safe (-ly), salute, welfare, (X all is, be) well, X wholly."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3073\">H3073</a>, <a href=\"#/H4918\">H4918</a>, <a href=\"#/H4919\">H4919</a>, <a href=\"#/H4920\">H4920</a>, <a href=\"#/H4921\">H4921</a>, <a href=\"#/H4922\">H4922</a>, <a href=\"#/H7966\">H7966</a>, <a href=\"#/H7967\">H7967</a>, <a href=\"#/H7968\">H7968</a>, <a href=\"#/H7999\">H7999</a>, <a href=\"#/H8002\">H8002</a>, <a href=\"#/H8003\">H8003</a>, <a href=\"#/H8004\">H8004</a>, <a href=\"#/H8005\">H8005</a>, <a href=\"#/H8006\">H8006</a>, <a href=\"#/H8010\">H8010</a>, <a href=\"#/H8011\">H8011</a>, <a href=\"#/H8013\">H8013</a>, <a href=\"#/H8015\">H8015</a>, <a href=\"#/H8016\">H8016</a>, <a href=\"#/H8017\">H8017</a>, <a href=\"#/H8018\">H8018</a>, <a href=\"#/H8019\">H8019</a>, <a href=\"#/H8020\">H8020</a>, <a href=\"#/H8021\">H8021</a>, <a href=\"#/H8022\">H8022</a>"}]}